% Demo purpose: show limited deterministic Detector and Energy-grid checks.
% Expected findings: SG021, SG022, SG023, and SG024 ERROR findings.
% Geometry settings: not required for this demo step.
% Scope: independently written, simplified, and not a production reactor model.

ene reversed_grid 2 0 10.0 1.0

det flux_detector de missing_grid dx 2.0 -2.0 0
det flux_detector de reversed_grid
